    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Very small women's bags for carrying personal articles, often of soft materials or beadwork, originally with a drawstring closure and carried around the wrist or in the hand.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
